		LNKSCH.CCL file.  NOTE: the  values are  all given  in
		OCTAL so add in OCTAL.
		
STEP 10		EDIT the  LNKSCH.CCL file  to reflect  this new  start
		value for the  overlapped PSECT.  Go back  to STEP  6.
